{"tid":1380034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪要做啲政治正確既事？","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T05:06:35.000Z","uid":706,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf8d00cbe206e7be8a7b2f46a0dd7b820f7f03d","tid":1380034,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:16:13.000Z","msg":"可能好on9，我都唔知有無用，但純粹由個玩法去諗<br />\n<br />\n國際基本承認香港係中國既一部分，依家港府管治失效，政治正確上我地係應該向國家主席求助，要求佢回應<br />\n大家都預計到佢唔會應/強烈譴責，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">咁樣會唔會令外國有機會以人道理由介入？依家習大大就係以&rdquo;內政&rdquo;、港府處理緊為理由阻止外國，但如果香港人直接求助，佢唔應或者點應都好，絕對有位外國入。</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然依家大家都心知肚明件事係點，但係有啲野始終要跟玩法，既然大家都唔擔心解放軍黎，依個方法可唔可行？"},{"pid":"950980e7bc359338cb5410a9512e3568b657dae6","tid":1380034,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ec357247f50e4ecfb60a9f01d0b8f06ca4b1207","tid":1380034,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:18:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fac2a1d268748036bd48212a5155c46dd92d4a73","tid":1380034,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:18:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dffadb23a96f82e33448309292bcb22218849675","tid":1380034,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:19:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f657453fc17555c712acce91beb0a7dd3a233a13","tid":1380034,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c2a63837c4ce304f471abcc6211b7733f01e0a9","tid":1380034,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f4ef6db554cf60e0af655529546aa5004a4c0d1","tid":1380034,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:19:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f063df6063facbfa5aca6e9e063cb47d09b595f","tid":1380034,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:20:00.000Z","msg":"推